node.text:
BOOTY BURNER 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Ending the weekend with a killer glute sesh 🥵 I wanted to finish my workout off with some accessory style movements to really burnout my muscles, and boy did I 😅 These may look 
simple, but I promise you, you will feel the burn 🔥
.
Give these a try on your next glute day! 👏🏼
.
1️⃣ Squat jump pulse - 4x10
2️⃣ Sumo Squat walks - 4x20 sec
3️⃣ Stagger stance lunge - 4x15 each leg
4️⃣ Side lunge slides - 4x20
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn
_____________________________

node.text:
LOWER ABS 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Oouufff this one had my belly burnin’ 🥵 Ended today’s lift with some outdoor abs ☀️ Trying to take advantage of the sunshine in between these rain storms ☔️ gotta love the rainy season 🥲
.
If you’re looking for a killer challenge, give these exercises a try! You can either do this as a circuit or individually! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Bird dog - 3x15 each side

.

.

node.text:
UNDER BOOTY 🍑
.
TAG a friend!
.
I hope everyone had a great start to their week! 🤗
.
When I was younger, I used to dreaddd Monday’s 😩 but now, I honestly love them! 😂 Weekends are very much needed but I love feeling productive and having that fresh start to the week feeling, knowing so much will be accomplished throughout the upcoming days 👏🏼 
.
Is it just me or does anyone else feel like this? 🙈😅
.
Anyways, here are a few of my favorites movements from today’s lift that you can incorporate into your next glute workout! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ SDL variation - 4x10 each leg
2️⃣ Yoga ball thrusts - 4x20
3️⃣ Half lunge/kickback pulse - 3x20 each leg 
4️⃣ Seated good mornings - 3x15
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn ~coral contour leggings, white axis bra~
Launching: July 17th 10am est 
_________________________

node.text:
HOME ABS ✨
.
TAG a friend!
.
Duke would give up all of his doggy toys just to have one car toy, specifically a mouse 😂 but I don’t think the kitties are amused 🙈 lol
.
Did a little home ab workout today and wanted to share! This is perfect to do as an add on to your workout, or to do just to get your body moving if you’re stuck at home 🤗 You can do these as a circuit or individually! 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Weighted leg raises - 3x15
2️⃣ Bridge hold/extension- 3x20
3️⃣ Oblique crunch variation - 3x20 each side 
4️⃣ Scissor variation - 3x30 sec
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn

node.text:
SUMMER BURN 🔥 
.
TAG a friend!
.
If you’re looking for a killer sweat sesh, this one’s for you 👏🏼🥵 If you want a quick cardio workout, you can easily make this into a circuit that you can do anywhere, anytime! Or you can add this to finish off any workout for a full body burnout 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Squat /oblique crunch - 4x20
2️⃣ Reverse lunge jump variation - 4x10 each leg
3️⃣ Jumping jack variation - 4x30 sec
4️⃣ Bicycle crunch variation - 4x15
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn
_________________________

node.text:
Eeeeek I’m screaming!! 😆🙈!!
.
Our first ever billboard in Times Square, NY 🎉!! I had so many emotions yesterday because never did I ever think that when we started this company almost 3 years ago out of our little studio apartment, that we would end up here 🙏🏼
.
We are beyond grateful for this opportunity and for the amazing family we’re building with all of you! 🥰 Thank you for the endless amounts of support and love, it truly means the world to us 💗 We have so many exciting things planned for the rest of the year and I cannot WAIT to show you 😍👏🏼
____________________________

KILLER LEGS 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Looking for a killer leg circuit? This one’s for you 👏🏼
. 
Finished off today’s leg day with these super 🔥 exercises and boy were my lil legs burnin’ 🥵 if you’re looking to spice up your workout, I highly recommend giving these a try on your next leg day 💪🏼
.
1️⃣ Static lunge - 3x15 each leg
2️⃣ Good mornings - 3x20
3️⃣ Squat jump variation- 3x15
4️⃣ Squat/reverse lunge - 3x20 each leg
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn ~charcoal agility bra, burnt orange pro shorts~
__________________________

node.text:
INNER THIGHS 🔥
.
TAG a friend!
.
Took the last week off to spend much needed time with family 🤗 Life has been insanely busy lately, so it felt nice to detach a little and enjoy their company! 😌
.
Now, it’s back to business 💪🏼! Had a great leg workout today and ended it with some inner thigh training! Here are some of my go-to movements that really fire up those inner thighs 🥵 Definitely give these a try on your next leg day!
.
1️⃣ Standing cable adduction - 3x15 each leg
2️⃣ Lying cable adduction- 3x20 each leg
3️⃣ Diagonal chop - 3x20 each leg
4️⃣ Kneeling cable adduction - 3x15 each leg
.
@brettstir 🎥💕
Outfit- @nvgtn
__________________________
